www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>也将推出该游戏，但这些版本的更新将在适当的时候发布。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/you-can-now-play-dark-souls-with-a-nostalgic-pixelated-demaster-3542562"><em>《黑暗之魂》</em>被一位改装者赋予了怀旧的“解大师”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/steam-next-fest-winner-enshrouded-announces-early-access-date-3530244">Steam Next Fest 获胜者“Enshrouded”宣布抢先体验日期，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
