</a>一起共同主持后一场活动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/pj-harvey-i-inside-the-old-year-dying-review-3465062">《I Inside The Old Year Dying》</a>是哈维的第十张录音室专辑，于七月发行。她最近结束了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pj-harvey-shares-single-i-inside-the-old-i-dying-and-announces-uk-and-european-tour-buy-tickets-3452462">英国和爱尔兰的头条巡演</a>，并于 10 月 31 日完成了欧洲行程。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="63" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/pj-harvey-live-in-manchester-setlist-photos-johnny-marr-3509087"><b>PJ Harvey 曼彻斯特演唱会：一场充满掐自己时刻的演出</b></a></li></ul><p><i>NME</i>在对 10 月 3 日这位创作型歌手在曼彻斯特的演出（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-johnny-marr-join-pj-harvey-on-stage-in-manchester-3508844">她与约翰尼·马尔一起登台</a>） <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/pj-harvey-live-in-manchester-setlist-photos-johnny-marr-3509087">进行了五星级评价</a>时表示，这场演出“充满了掐自己的时刻”。</p><p>它继续说道：“哈维从来都不是一个会迎合演奏她的热门歌曲的人，但在这里，策展对粉丝来说就像一个宝库：充满了复活节彩蛋和特殊的稀有物品。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pj-harvey-announces-huge-outdoor-london-show-for-summer-2024-buy-tickets-3519734">哈维此后宣布明年八月将在伦敦古纳斯伯里公园举办户外音乐会</a>- <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fpj-harvey-tickets%2Fartist%2F945172%3Firgwc%3D1%26utm_source%3D2862475-NME%2520Networks%2520Media%2520Limited%26utm_medium%3Daffiliate%26utm_campaign%3D2862475%26awtrc%3D%26clickId%3DzdmQRZTfwxyNUAZWPp1MB0h4UkFTZES1nUsmUU0%26camefrom%3DCFC_BUYAT_2862475%26ircid%3D7559">在这里查找剩余的门票</a>。在其他新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/n